body.p: Fraction absorbed, i.e., only a fraction of the empagliflozin in the intestinal lumen is absorbed. This parameter determines how much of the empagliflozin is excreted.
F_emp_abs of dose is absorbed. (1-F_emp_abs) is excreted in feces.
Swallowing, dissolution of tablet, and transport into intestine. Overall process describing the rates of this processes.
